---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service | BareCanvas"
  description="Terms of Service for BareCanvas - Professional waxing services in Pearland, TX. Review our policies for appointments, cancellations, and service expectations."
>
  <div class="terms-of-service">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="terms-header">
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: September 5, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <div class="terms-content">
        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>By booking an appointment or using our services at BareCanvas, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use our services.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>2. Service Description</h2>
          <p>BareCanvas provides professional waxing services including but not limited to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Full body waxing services</li>
            <li>Facial waxing</li>
            <li>Specialized waxing treatments</li>
            <li>Skin care consultations</li>
          </ul>
          <p>All services are performed by licensed professionals in a clean, safe environment.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>3. Booking and Appointments</h2>
          <h3>Appointment Scheduling</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Appointments must be booked in advance through our online system or by phone</li>
            <li>We require a valid phone number and email address for appointment confirmations</li>
            <li>First-time clients may be required to complete a consultation form</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>Arrival Policy</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Please arrive 10 minutes early for your appointment</li>
            <li>Late arrivals (more than 15 minutes) may result in rescheduling or shortened service time</li>
            <li>We reserve the right to cancel appointments for no-shows</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>4. Cancellation and Rescheduling Policy</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>24-Hour Notice:</strong> Appointments must be cancelled or rescheduled at least 24 hours in advance</li>
            <li><strong>Same-Day Cancellations:</strong> May result in a 50% service fee charge</li>
            <li><strong>No-Shows:</strong> Will be charged the full service amount</li>
            <li><strong>Emergency Situations:</strong> Will be handled on a case-by-case basis</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We understand emergencies happen and will work with you when possible.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>5. Payment Terms</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Payment is due at the time of service</li>
            <li>We accept cash, credit cards, and digital payments</li>
            <li>Prices are subject to change with 30 days notice</li>
            <li>Gratuities are appreciated but not required</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>6. Health and Safety Requirements</h2>
          <h3>Client Responsibilities</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Inform us of any medications, skin conditions, or allergies</li>
            <li>Do not book if you have active infections, open wounds, or sunburn</li>
            <li>Avoid sun exposure 24 hours before and after waxing</li>
            <li>Follow pre and post-care instructions provided</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>Our Commitments</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Use only high-quality, professional-grade products</li>
            <li>Maintain strict sanitation and hygiene standards</li>
            <li>Provide a clean, safe, and comfortable environment</li>
            <li>Respect client privacy and confidentiality</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>7. Refunds and Satisfaction</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>We strive for 100% client satisfaction</li>
            <li>If you're unsatisfied, please contact us within 48 hours</li>
            <li>Refunds are handled on a case-by-case basis</li>
            <li>Touch-up services may be offered instead of refunds</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>8. Liability and Disclaimers</h2>
          <h3>Service Risks</h3>
          <p>Waxing services may involve risks including but not limited to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Temporary skin irritation or redness</li>
            <li>Ingrown hairs</li>
            <li>Allergic reactions (rare)</li>
            <li>Skin lifting (if using certain medications)</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>Limitation of Liability</h3>
          <p>BareCanvas liability is limited to the cost of the service provided. We are not responsible for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>9. Privacy and Confidentiality</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>We protect your personal and health information</li>
            <li>Information is only shared as necessary for service delivery</li>
            <li>Photography or testimonials require explicit consent</li>
            <li>Please review our Privacy Policy for detailed information</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>10. Code of Conduct</h2>
          <p>We expect all clients to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Treat our staff with respect and courtesy</li>
            <li>Follow hygiene requirements</li>
            <li>Arrive in appropriate condition for service</li>
            <li>Communicate openly about comfort levels and concerns</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We reserve the right to refuse service for inappropriate behavior.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>11. Modifications to Terms</h2>
          <p>We may update these Terms of Service from time to time. Changes will be posted on our website with an updated effective date. Continued use of our services constitutes acceptance of updated terms.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>12. Contact Information</h2>
          <p>For questions about these Terms of Service or to resolve any issues, please contact us:</p>
          <div class="contact-info">
            <p><strong>BareCanvas</strong></p>
            <p>2743 Smith Ranch Rd, Suite 804<br>
            Pearland, TX 77584</p>
            <p>Phone: <a href="tel:+18325709458">(832) 570-9458</a></p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@barecanvastx.com">info@barecanvastx.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="terms-section">
          <h2>13. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These Terms of Service are governed by the laws of the State of Texas. Any disputes will be resolved in the courts of Harris County, Texas.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .terms-of-service {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f4f0 0%, #e8ddd4 100%);
    padding: 120px 0 80px;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .terms-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .terms-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #8B4513;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: #666;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .terms-content {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 40px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.1);
  }

  .terms-section {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .terms-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .terms-section h2 {
    color: #8B4513;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #D2B48C;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .terms-section h3 {
    color: #8B4513;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 25px 0 15px 0;
  }

  .terms-section p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #444;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .terms-section ul {
    margin: 15px 0;
    padding-left: 25px;
  }

  .terms-section li {
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #444;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .terms-section li strong {
    color: #8B4513;
  }

  .contact-info {
    background: #f8f4f0;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8B4513;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .contact-info a {
    color: #8B4513;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-info a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .terms-of-service {
      padding: 100px 0 60px;
    }

    .terms-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .terms-content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }

    .terms-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .terms-section h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>